data.description: Stunning 3 bedroom PLUS loft end unit townhome! Meticulously maintained & updated by the original owner, move right in! Open & bright with all the windows only found in an end unit! The main level features the living room with gleaming hardwood floors & gas log fireplace with elegant hearth. Informal dining area with ceiling fan plus breakfast bar. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, pantry, a Bosch dishwasher & new garbage disposal. Also half bath & access to the garage. The upstairs loft has incredible built-ins, perfect for your home office! The primary bedroom has a vaulted ceiling with fan, huge walk-in closet & private, 3/4 bath with tile floor.  Two additional bedrooms plus a full bath with tile floor. Full laundry room with washer, dryer, cabinet storage & hanging bar! 2 car garage with amazing storage! Quiet, residential neighborhood with common areas, play park & lush green spaces! Easy access to Hwy’s plus all the great shopping & restaurants Maple Grove offers!
